  AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM "Question" q2 WHERE q2."examId" = e.id AND q2.stem = $patch$When publishing a workbook to Tableau Server, an analyst wants to ensure that an embedded data source credential is stored on the server so that scheduled extract refreshes can run without user intervention. Which credential option in the publish dialog achieves this?$patch$);
