         $json$[{"id":"a","text":"Set"},{"id":"b","text":"Group"},{"id":"c","text":"Parameter"},{"id":"d","text":"Context Filter"}]$json$::jsonb, $json$["c"]$json$::jsonb, $patch$Parameters are user-editable single values that are not tied to any field and can be referenced in calculated fields, filters, or reference lines. Sets define dynamic or static collections of dimension members, Groups combine members into categories, and Context Filters affect filter evaluation order. The source states: 'Parameters: user-editable single value; not tied to any field; controlled via UI.'$patch$, $patch$Explore and Analyze Data$patch$,
         3, $json$[{"url":"https://help.tableau.com/current/pro/desktop/en-us/parameters_create.htm","label":"Tableau Parameters"}]$json$::jsonb, 'DRAFT'::"QStatus", 'claude-sonnet-4-6', false, NOW(), NOW()
